1. The 2-year overall survival rate was 56% in the twice-daily group.
2. The 95% confidence interval for the 2-year survival rate in the twice-daily group was 50–62%.
3. The 2-year overall survival rate was 51% in the once-daily group.
4. The 95% confidence interval for the 2-year survival rate in the once-daily group was 45–57%.
5. The absolute difference in 2-year survival rates between the treatment groups was 5.3%.
6. The 95% confidence interval for the absolute difference in 2-year survival rates between the treatment groups was -3.2% to 13.7%.
